the \fI\%CROSSCOMPILING_EMULATOR\fP target property unconditionally.
The \fBNEW\fP behavior for this policy is for \fI\%add_test()\fP to use
the \fI\%CROSSCOMPILING_EMULATOR\fP target property only when
\fI\%cross\-compiling\fP\&.
