.sp
\fI\%USE_FOLDERS\fP global property is treated as \fBON\fP by default.
.sp
When using CMake 3.25 or earlier, \fI\%USE_FOLDERS\fP is treated
as \fBOFF\fP by default unless projects enable the feature.  For example:
